data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom townhouse with a versatile loft in the heart of Woodstock. The owner's suite is conveniently situated on the main level, adjacent to a full bathroom for added convenience. Upstairs, a spacious and versatile loft area offers endless possibilities, whether you envision it as a home office, a kid/teen space, or a cozy library. The open concept living area creates a warm and inviting space for both everyday living and entertaining, seamlessly connecting the living room and kitchen. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and offers a view into the living room, with easy access to the sunny back patio. Additionally, you'll find an attached 1-car garage and driveway. Located in close proximity to Hobgood Park and just minutes from Little River and JD's on the Lake, this townhouse provides easy access to outdoor activities and family fun. Schedule a showing today to explore the charm and potential of this fantastic townhouse!
